<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_04_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema611_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_04_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              다슬기 풀어 주기 행사를 위해 다슬기
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </div>
              &nbsp;t을 트럭 2대에 똑같이 나누어 실었습니다. 트럭 한 대에 실은 다슬기의 양은 몇 t인지
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">알아봅시다.</div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1"> 
          <div class="flex align_start">
            <div class="picture_wrap">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 1370 973" fill="none">
                <text transform="matrix(0.996569 0.0827626 -0.169304 0.985564 1025.09 310)" fill="#222222" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard" font-size="24" font-weight="bold" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                  <tspan x="0.386719" y="26.784">다슬기 풀어 주기</tspan>
                </text>
              </svg>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0003_content.png" alt="" />
              <button class="zoom"></button>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area">
              <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>
            
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(9)-:2" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2"> 
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="img_box">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0003_content2.png" alt="" />

              <span class="txt txt1">1 (t)</span>
              <span class="txt txt2">0</span>
              <span class="txt txt3">÷2</span>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area">
              <h3 lang="y">
                트럭 한 대에 실은 다슬기의 양을 구하는 방법을 생각해 보고 그림을<br>
                이용하여 알아보세요.
              </h3>
            
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                  <div class="example_box">
                    <p lang="y">
                      <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>9</span></span>
                      <span>를 똑같이 2로 나눈 것 중 하나이므로 트럭 한 대에 실은</span>
                    </p>
                    <p lang="y">
                      <span>다슬기의 양은</span>
                      <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>9</span></span>
                      <span>t 입니다.</span>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">트럭 한 대에 실은 다슬기의 양은 몇 t인가요?</h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="question_box justify_center gap_8">
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(9)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>t</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_4">
          <h3 lang="y">
            <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
              <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                4÷2를 이용하여
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </span>
                ÷2를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
              </div>
            </div>
          </h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="question_box justify_center gap_4">
              <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>9</span></span>
              <span>÷2=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box gap_20">
                <span class="flex align_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="4" text-align="center"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>÷</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2" text-align="center"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>9</span>
              </span>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(9)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="img_box">
              <div class="text" lang="y">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_6">
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>9</span></span>
                  <span>는</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>9</span></span>
                  <span>이</span>
                </div>
                <span>4개인 수야.</span>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0003_char.png" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
